unittitle_ssm: Records of the Office of the President (John Crittenden Sawhill)
abstract_ssm: The Papers of John Crittenden Sawhill include materials generated during the years 1974 – 1981, including selected materials created in the Office of the President by Acting President Ivan Loveridge Bennett Jr., 1979 – 1981, as well as some created elsewhere within the University community dating from as early as 1955. The papers have been divided into eleven series and two addenda.
